## User Authentication API (Node.js + Express + MongoDB)

This project provides a simple authentication API using Node.js, Express, Mongoose (MongoDB), and JWT tokens. It supports registration, login, protected routes, and token-based access.

## The API supports:

User Registration

User Login (Token Generation)

Fetch Logged-in User Data

Fetch All Users (protected)


## Detailed documentation for each API endpoint in Postman.
## Postman Link:
