## API Endpoints

## POST /api/auth/register

Register a user

Request: { username, email, password }

Response: { message }

## POST /api/auth/login

Log in user

Request: { email, password }

Response: { token }

## GET /api/auth/me

Get current user (token required)

## GET /api/auth/users

Get all users (token required)

## Validation & Error Handling
All inputs are validated (e.g., empty fields return errors).

Duplicate emails are blocked during registration.

Invalid logins return clear error messages.

All passwords are hashed using bcryptjs.